<title>USA: Community Care evaluates acquisition deals.</title>
<headline>Community Care evaluates acquisition deals.</headline>
<dateline>NAPLES, Fla. 1997-06-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>Community Care of America Inc said on Friday that it is evaluating several &quot;expressions of interest from potential acquirers&quot; with its financial advisor, Smith Barney.</p>
<p>The board of directors of Community Care has established a special committee, with delegated authority to oversee the process of selling the company and entertain any offer to maximize shareholder value, the company said.</p>
